items.bio: If I were to be an actor, I'd love to act in a tearjerker movie.
Fun loving, meeting new people, enjoy foods and exchanging conversations with all walks of life.
Enjoy life and earn sufficient money that is all I am bother about:)
Film/TV producer. Author of 2 books,"I Liked It, Didn't Love It (Screenplay Development From The Inside Out)"&"The Complete Filmmaker's Guide to Film Festivals"
